definitions.definition: ( intransitive , Internet , informal ) To use the internet; specifically, to search for information by using the internet.
examples: Having no idea what that means, I am internetting like mad.

main_definition: ( intransitive , Internet , informal ) To use the internet; specifically, to search for information by using the internet.

definitions.definition: To entwine or link (several things) together , so as to form a network ; to interconnect , to network .
To connect (a computer , an electronic device , etc.) into a computer network (in particular, the Internet ).

main_definition: ( archaic , rare ) To entwine or link (several things) together , so as to form a network ; to interconnect , to network .
secondary_definitions: ( specifically , networking ) To connect (a computer , an electronic device , etc.) into a computer network (in particular, the Internet ).
